{"tid":2388291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地有幾耐冇聽過願榮光歸香港?","createTime":"2021-01-31T04:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T12:28:23.000Z","uid":10905,"like":235,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"15a15d0c22f0a9d737709cbe468b5adf05d6915e","tid":2388291,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5huSvBMa8YA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5huSvBMa8YA&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=1b42e96f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5huSvBMa8YA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=ed0fccff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n一路睇住條片<br />\n一路諗起香港慢慢步向衰落<br />\n諗番起所有畫面<br />\n即刻喊撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記犧牲左既手足<br />\n唔好忘記仲有好多手足被港共迫害緊<br />\n同埋被送中既10位手足<br />\n<br />\n光復香港。時代革命"},{"pid":"c21a7534549764a7f964dd301b7c3f1c1648aac4","tid":2388291,"uid":169918,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"喺屋企日日都聽"},{"pid":"28b7a8ae79cca5c510c0ca18b2cb8cbba55cc285","tid":2388291,"uid":44367,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"好耐好耐......會想喊 <br />\n<br />\n香港人最團結既時候 沒齒難忘"},{"pid":"ed7b7b19a19e0900d821c02a65f59ec296550d94","tid":2388291,"uid":10241,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"尋日搭車先聽完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲用緊黎明來到果段做聆聲同鬧鐘聲<br />\n一出街電話響比人望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc8f49bd7fe078afaa9e80402076aa51cd5f1f4","tid":2388291,"uid":237459,"like":14,"dislike":38,"score":-24,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"